column2: select count(s.bestObjID) as num_objs, avg(e.zerr/e.z) as mean_fzerr from wise_xmatch as xm  join SpecObjAll as s on xm.sdss_objid = s.bestObjID  join PhotoObjAll as p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objID  join emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID = e.specObjID  join wise_allsky as w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr where xm.match_dist<=# and s.zwarning=# and e.z># and e.zerr/e.z<=# and e.z<=# and w.w1cc_map=# and w.w2cc_map=# and w.w3cc_map=# and w.w4cc_map=# and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det1<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det2<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det3<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and w.ph_qual_det4<># and s.class=&&& and s.subClass=&&& and (w.w1mpro-w.w2mpro)>=# and e.Flux_OIII_#<># and e.Flux_OIII_#>e.Flux_OIII_#_Err
